data.description: This cute cottage with sprawling front porch is nestled on almost an acre in the heart of Mobile. The entryway invites you in to a large family room; perfect for entertaining.  The two bedrooms are both nice size. One featuring a closet and desk space while the other offers three closets and a lounge nook; perfect for curling up with a good book. The kitchen is located towards the back of the home and has tons of painted cabinets, gas range, microwave, and recently added mini dishwasher.  The dining room is currently in the kitchen, but there is a small, keeping room off the kitchen that could also function as a dining space and offers views of the backyard. The partially wooded backyard, offers privacy, shade, and even walking trails. If you are one who likes to work on projects there are two small workshops with power. The laundry room is located outside in a separate structure and does offer an additional full bath. Looking to own your first home, or perhaps downsize but still wanting a great private yard? come check this place out! All measurements are approximate and not guaranteed, buyer to verify.
